    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-08-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-08-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="1400"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1400">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 (Potsdam)/8–145</note>
                <head>No. 1400<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CJ1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caffery</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the French Minister of Foreign Affairs</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_BG1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bidault</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/> No. 678</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-08-01">August 1,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: I have just received a communication from
                    Potsdam by telephone<note n="1" xml:id="d1400fn1">A copy of the instruction to
                        the British Ambassador at Paris to make a similar approach to the French
                        Government bears the following manuscript notation: “Telephoned <persName
                            corresp="#p_CJ1">Caffery</persName> Aug 1, 6:00 p.m.”</note> from the
                    Secretary of State instructing me to communicate to the Government of France a
                    statement which has been adopted by the Three Powers at the Conference
                    concerning the trial of <gloss target="#t_War1">war</gloss> criminals.</p>
                <p>You will note that the three Governments will be most grateful if the French
                    Government will treat the present communication as strictly secret until such
                    time as an official statement is issued by the Conference.</p>
                <p>I avail myself [etc.]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_CJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Jefferson Caffery</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#center">[Enclosure]</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#left">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        </seg>
                    </opener>
                    <p>[Here is set forth, with minor variations, the text of <ref target="#d1383"
                            >document No. 1383</ref>, section VII (VI).]</p>
                    <p>It is the earnest wish of the three Governments that the Provisional
                        Government of the French Republic will be able to associate itself with the
                        above statement.</p>
                    <p>The three Governments would be grateful if the French Provisional Government
                        would treat the present communication as strictly secret until such time as
                        an official statement is issued by the Conference.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <dateline rendition="#left">
                            <placeName>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                            </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-08-01">August 1,
                                1945</date>.</dateline>
                    </closer>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
